sequenceDiagram
  participant L as Agent Loop
  participant C as Catalog
  participant D as Discovery Policy
  participant M as Model
  participant TS as ToolSearch
  participant P as Tool Pipeline
  participant E as Event Log

  L->>C: Read candidate capabilities
  L->>D: Enter tasks/paths/permissions/budget/connection status
  D-->>L: visible set
  L->>E: capability.diff
  L->>M: messages + visible tools + skill index
  M-->>L: intent: search capability
  L->>TS: Query candidate capabilities
  TS-->>D: Candidate results
  D-->>L: update visible set
  L->>M: Expose new capabilities
  M-->>L: intent: call tool
  L->>P: validate / permission / execute / observe
  P-->>E: tool event + observation
